deck: In ORIGINS #2, hostages have been taken and a bomb threat issued at the 30 St. Mary Axe in downtown London. The situation is tense, but Atlas is on his way to save the day! Taking down the armed guards is like a walk in the park, but can he get to the trigger man before the bomb goes off?

In ORIGINS #3, In the third installment of the Atlas:ORIGINS series, our hero returns to the Earth Temple to seek the guidance of his teacher, Gaya. Then, a tense scene unfolds in a remote military compound in North Korea, where a young captive is not at all what she seems to be. Plus, the full reveal of Atlas' first major villain - PULSAR! The villains are rising all around Atlas, gearing up for the next action-packed issue next month!
